title: Power.Retouche.v7.3.retail.for.Adobe.Photoshop.rar
description:
Power Retouche Pro v7.3 retail - Photoshop plugin [from F.O.S.I] + tutorials

Equalizer

Dynamic Range Compressor

Lens Corrector
Soft-filter
Sharpness Editor
Black definition
Golden Section
Illumination Editor
Radial density Corrector
Contrast Editor
Exposure Corrector
Color Corrector
White-balance Corrector

I have added all the .pdf tutorials for each plugin to this download archive. Enjoy!
